bans.title: If game was draft mode, contains banned champion data, otherwise null

baronKills.title: Number of times the team killed baron

dominionVictoryScore.title: If game was a dominion game, specifies the points the team had at game end, otherwise null

dragonKills.title: Number of times the team killed dragon

firstBaron.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team got the first baron kill

firstBlood.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team got first blood

firstDragon.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team got the first dragon kill

firstInhibitor.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team destroyed the first inhibitor

firstTower.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team destroyed the first tower

inhibitorKills.title: Number of inhibitors the team destroyed

towerKills.title: Number of towers the team destroyed

vilemawKills.title: Number of times the team killed vilemaw

winner.title: Flag indicating whether or not the team won
